text: Naushad Iqbal (born 16 February 2002) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. he was selected 16 February 2018 in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Twenty20 Cricket League Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan cricket team draft list. On 25 February 2019, he made his T20 debut for the Bangladesh Sports Education Institute cricket team in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Twenty20 Cricket League, taking one wicket for seventeen runs. He made his List A cricket debut on 8 March 2019 for the Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan cricket team in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:2002 births Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Living people
